  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduo a kColorPicker</title>

    <para>
      kColorPicker is a QToolButton library with a color popup menu, which lets
you select colors. The popup menu features a color dialog button which can
be used to add custom colors to the popup menu.
    </para>

    &lfs113_checked;

